<w:widowControl w:val="0"/><w:sz w:val="22"/><w:szCs w:val="22"/>It would be recommended that xxxxx be issues with a portable heater to be positioned at her workstation to provide heat to her immediate surrounding.  
<w:widowControl w:val="0"/><w:spacing w:line="24pt" w:lineRule="auto"/><w:sz w:val="22"/><w:szCs w:val="22"/>9. Other issues
<w:widowControl w:val="0"/><w:sz w:val="22"/><w:szCs w:val="22"/>As highlighted, xxxxx uses her handwritten notes at her workstation but in doing so obtains a poor posture. It would be recommended that she be supplied with a document/writing slope. This would be positioned between her keyboard and screens, with its default position being a document holder. If required to write the slope slides over her keyboard, allowing the correct posture to still be maintained. Once finished the slope magnetically clicks back into position. 
